overview: Kiara Cole and Vina Sky - For Vina`s birthday, Kiara has a sexy, sultry surprise. Blindfolded, Vina lets Kiara lead her into the bedroom. When Kiara takes the blindfold away, Vina is treated to the sight of Jake on the bed with his junk in a box. Best. Birthday. Party. Ever.Bunny Colby and Kiara Cole - Bunny has plenty of fantasies that prove she bats for both teams. She may have a boyfriend at the moment, but Bunny dreams of watching him fuck another girl. She finally gets her opportunity when her college friend, Kiara, comes for a visit.
tagline: Feel free to bring a friend!
title: Plus One
